Print working directory              ----                 $  pwd

Shutdown                             ----                 $  shutdown now

List directory contents              ----                 $  ls


Get list of all entered 
commands in terminal                 ----                 $  history

clearing the terminal screen         ----                 $  clear

show directory/file path that contains 
all commands entered in terminal     ----                 $  echo $HISTFILE

one step rollback in directory       ----                 $  cd ..

go to home directory from anywhere   ----                 $  cd

current date and time                ----                 $ date
present  calendar                    ----                 $ cal


sleep 10s && mplayer ~/Downloads/'Mirzapur- Extended Theme Song _ OST _ Amazon Prime.mp3'
